com.intellij.util.xml

Annotation Type ExtendClass


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface ExtendClass
    Annotates DOM methods that return either PsiClass or GenericDomValue<PsiClass>. Specifies that the references class should extend some other class (or implement interface). If this doesn't happen, error will appear.
    See Also:
